Trinity::

She walked over and put a paw on Windlord. "You look like you need 
some energy. I'm out of energon cubes, but I'll give you some of 
mine. I don't mind. Besides, I got plenty of energy." She ran around 
really fast in a circle for a few seconds. "See? I can spare some."
